profile:
Fibrenew Fraser Valley specializes in the repair, restoration and renewal of leather, plastics, vinyl, fabric and upholstery servicing six major markets: automotive, aviation, commercial, medical, marine and residential. Utilizing our services to repair damaged materials in your vehicle, boat, airplane, home or office offers an environmentally-friendly and cost-effective alternative to replacement.

Leather Repair, Vinyl Restoration and Plastic Renewal Services in:
Abbotsford, British Columbia; Chilliwack, British Columbia; Hope, British Columbia

Look at before/after photos of our amazing repair work: www.fibrenew.com/fraser_valley/photos/

profile: K.D.C. provides an innovative approach to furniture refurbishment and interior design...it's all about branding yourself into your spaces. We guide you through bringing out your best colours and most exciting ideas: it's a collaboration and we is full of brilliant ideas designed to enhance your spaces in ways that reverberate YOU. Through the refurbishment, revamp and personalisation of existing furniture we work to make changes that are not only uniquely you, but are also fun and affordable. We offer colour consultations for your home or office and will guide you through making some exciting changes. With years of experience in interior design and decor, K.D.C. will assist should new or additional finishes and furnishings be needed.
